\begin_layout Standard
算子范数
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Proposition 3.8.2
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
线性映射
\begin_inset Formula $T:E\to F$
\end_inset

连续, iff, 它有界.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
有界算子空间, 有界线性泛函, 对偶空间.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Proposition 3.8.3
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $E,F$
\end_inset

是赋范空间.
 则
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
1.
 
\begin_inset Formula $B(E,F)$
\end_inset

关于算子范数是赋范线性空间;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
2.
 若
\begin_inset Formula $T:E\to F$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $S:F\to G$
\end_inset

均是有界线性映射, 则
\begin_inset Formula $ST:E\to G$
\end_inset

也是有界线性映射, 且
\begin_inset Formula $\norm{ST}\le\norm{S}\cdot\norm{T}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
3.
 若
\begin_inset Formula $F$
\end_inset

是完备的Banach空间, 则
\begin_inset Formula $B(E,F)$
\end_inset

也是完备的.
 特别地, 若
\begin_inset Formula $E$
\end_inset

是任意的赋范空间, 
\begin_inset Formula $E^{*}$
\end_inset

总是完备的.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Proposition 3.8.4
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $1\le p<\infty$
\end_inset

, 有
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{1}{p}+\frac{1}{q}=1$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $\ell^{p}$
\end_inset

的对偶空间典范同构于
\begin_inset Formula $\ell^{q}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
证明过程可以用来证
\begin_inset Formula $(\ell^{1})^{*}=\ell^{\infty}$
\end_inset

, 但
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\ell^{\infty}\right)^{*}\supseteq\ell^{1}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\ell^{\infty}$
\end_inset

是不好的空间, 因为它是不可分的.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
刻画
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\ell^{\infty}\right)^{*}$
\end_inset

需要超滤子, 超滤集和选择公理.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
然而使用弱拓扑研究
\begin_inset Formula $\ell^{\infty}$
\end_inset

是最自然的.
\end_layout

